WEBVTT

00:05.369 --> 00:08.295
Previously on Mystery Inc...

00:08.415 --> 00:10.453
The whole planispheric disc!

00:10.573 --> 00:12.756
I've *** together a rudimentary player

00:12.876 --> 00:14.264
for the planispheric disc.

00:14.384 --> 00:16.866
The sooner we find out
what this is supposed to do,

00:16.986 --> 00:19.202
the sooner we'll solve
the mystery of the *** treasure.

00:19.322 --> 00:20.528
Nibiru!

00:20.648 --> 00:21.724
Jeepers, Fred.

00:21.844 --> 00:24.104
You're living in a van, down by the river.

00:24.224 --> 00:25.373
I didn't have much choice.

00:25.493 --> 00:27.413
My folks got have 20 spare
bedrooms in the house

00:27.523 --> 00:29.886
and I'm sure if you moved in,
they wouldn't even notice!

00:30.596 --> 00:32.533
You and I should be okay in here.

00:32.653 --> 00:34.587
Nibiru has come!

00:34.707 --> 00:36.485
This has all happened before!

00:36.605 --> 00:38.332
It begins with the animal.

00:38.452 --> 00:40.334
The dog dies.

00:40.454 --> 00:43.000
Is he talking about me?

00:44.625 --> 00:47.173
If each of the pieces reveals a location,

00:47.293 --> 00:50.056
then all of the pieces together
should show us the treasure.

00:50.446 --> 00:51.382
Jeepers!

00:51.502 --> 00:53.398
It could be a cache of diamonds!

00:53.518 --> 00:54.438
In a gold trap!

00:54.558 --> 00:56.089
Covered in hot fudge!

00:56.209 --> 00:58.273
Like, wrapped in a burrito!

00:58.834 --> 01:01.226
What would be your opinion, Nova?

01:04.964 --> 01:06.131
Hmm?

01:09.235 --> 01:12.356
Jinkies, look at this, gang.

01:16.755 --> 01:19.499
"Senor P. Llave."

01:19.567 --> 01:21.369
Like, what kind
of name is that?

01:23.326 --> 01:25.491
And what's the deal
with the numbers?

01:25.559 --> 01:27.296
Maybe the numbers
are more coordinates.

01:27.364 --> 01:29.526
This could be the ultimate
treasure destination.

01:29.593 --> 01:32.152
We should be ready
to expect anything.

01:33.186 --> 01:34.947
You have to help me!

01:35.015 --> 01:36.511
Sheriff? What's wrong?

01:36.579 --> 01:38.579
We're in the middle
of a full-scale galactic war,

01:38.643 --> 01:40.981
and the earth is the prize.

